fields.post_content:
Why when i click a like and dislike button is take time to display.
How to fix it?
Very fun and exciting general education subject!

Enrolled in semester 1/year 2023 Anyone who can't register in time is advised to wait until the last day that registration opens.
- Names are checked every class.

Score collection: There are no midterm/final exams. But there may be an oral test.
The job is to collect 30 hours of running hours (work for the whole semester).
Studying with one teacher who is quite strict, studying in the morning is a little hot. Some of my friends didn't get A's. They got A's around 70%, but it may also depend on the teacher.
This class is very fun. The teacher is kind. He's just loud. Haha. We come to study online. The disadvantage is that the sun is very hot. It's recommended that you study after 4 p.m.
Try reading books for exams in the morning, trust me, it's twice as effective!!
